trans-unit.source: Defines the methods called during contract generation that can be used to modify the generated code for a service contract.
trans-unit.target: Definiuje metody wywołane podczas generowania kontraktu, który może służyć do modyfikowania wygenerowany kod dla kontraktu usługi.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IServiceContractGenerationExtension interface on a contract behavior (a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName> type) to enable you to modify the code generated when a contract or endpoint is compiled into code.
trans-unit.target: Zaimplementuj interfejs IServiceContractGenerationExtension zachowania kontraktu ( <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>typu) umożliwia modyfikowanie kodu generowane, gdy kontrakt lub punkt końcowy jest kompilowany do kodu.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> inserts a custom contract behavior into the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection during the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Zazwyczaj niestandardowych <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>wstawia zachowanie kontraktu niestandardowych do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kolekcji podczas wywołania <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A>lub <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Implement to modify the code document object model prior to the contract generation process.
trans-unit.target: Wdrożenie, aby zmodyfikować kod document object model przed proces generowania umowy.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName> to modify the contract, operations, or the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName> prior to code generation.
The code generated context to use to modify the code document prior to generation.
trans-unit.target: Kontekst do użycia, aby zmodyfikować dokument kodu przed generowania wygenerować kodu.
